title: 6 AM Hour - I Remember When That Song Came Out
description:
Happy Monday! Dave is LIVE from Boston a good chunk of this week but you can hardly tell! Falen is gearing up for her trip to Spain and we got a whole lot of laughs today!

Jenny's First Song of the Day: Come On Over - Christina Aguilera, Top Gun Call Signs, & More!
